parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.Welcome to Estero State Park. I’m Ranger Michael. You can just call me Michael.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiSaEx.I’m sad to say there are some renovations taking place and the trails are shut down. But you’re welcome to explore around this dried up creek bed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.That’s it? I can’t go on the trails? That’s lame.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.Please be patient with the parks department. As you know, Estero State park is the largest state park in the country, spanning hundreds of square miles.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.And yet, I’m limited to this one pond?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiBaEx.Sorry. I can’t let anyone pass through who isn’t certified to search the native ruins.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrOp.Every year new locations are being mapped out thanks to new lidar laser scans.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Woah! Cool! A lot has changed since I left here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoOp.My job is getting tough. So many looters these days. Especially since Sofia Vesper bought a mansion in the south side of town.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeShCl.What!? Sofia Vesper is moving to our town!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.That’s right. The world’s most famous treasure hunter is going to be calling Cape Vedra her home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.Well... I mean... She’s not the most famous treasure hunter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Idaho Johnson. He’s the most famous treasure hunter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrDe.Oh yeah! I almost forgot he existed. I wonder what he is up to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiBaOp.Too bad. That’s the life of a treasure hunter I suppose. A good reason to stay away from such a dirty profession.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.So what new sites have you all found in the last few years?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiBaEx.The same old stuff, just a lot more of it. Mostly native artifacts with some spanish artifacts mixed in.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoOp.The native talismans are fetching some money on the black market, but it’s illegal to take them from the park.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiBaEx.If you find one, alert the authorities.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.A park ranger... The natural enemy of the treasure hunter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.I better be careful not to get caught snooping around.");
Set Variable 101 to a value between 1 and 7
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I bet this is what Diana was talking about. I wonder if she would give me money for it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaOp.If it’s valuable enough... I could afford to remodel my new place and maybe fund my own expedition. Hell… This could make me rich! I should show it to her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.So you have permission from the park ranger to be here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Let me guess. You’re another one of his lunatic fans.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What are you doing here? Did you come for his funeral?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnCl.Listen kid. I’m not here to small talk. I have a serious job to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.From the sound of it she didn’t like my Dad too much. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.I remember when I was very young I met Dad in Peru and she was with him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.I don’t even know why I was there. I think I was vacationing with family and he stopped by.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaOp.It’s too fuzzy to recall. I was only maybe seven years old at the time. But I do remember Clare.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.And she still is... Hot damn she’s pretty as hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I wonder what she’s doing here now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.I found a jade talisman. Do you want to buy it for $140?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Weren’t those the goons from the bar?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrCl.I wanted to get away from the house for a while.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrOp.I don’t know about that. I can still see my house from here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.You’re a grown woman Alia. You don’t need permission to go for a walk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlSaCl.I know. But he is very protective of me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlSaOp.My Mom argues with my Dad sometimes. She wants me to get out more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Your Mom seems like a very bold woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlWoOp.She is. It drives Daddy nuts sometimes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlSaCl.Sometimes I think they would be happier apart. But I know they’ve stayed together for me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrCl.They do what they do because they love me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.It must be nice having something like that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrOp.Are you here to learn how to find treasure 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Keep it down Alia. You’re not allowed to hunt treasure here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.You know there is a cave a short walk from here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrOp.A pool inside a cave... That sounds interesting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlHaOp.Do you think there’s treasure in the cave?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrCl.Ok 1Hero. But let’s not be gone long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I should take Alia to the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I should take Alia to the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I should take Alia to the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrEx.I was just playing in the park here with my new friend.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SmShOp.You ran away from home to be with a boy?!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlSaOp.Daddy! Don’t be mad at 1Hero. It was my fault.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlAnEx.Nothing! All we did was go exploring.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SmAnOp.Alia. You go home right now. I was worried sick about you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SmAnDe.You listen here 1Hero. If that’s really your name.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SmAnDe.You better stay away from my daughter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.You can’t tell her what to do. She’s a grown woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "SmAnOp.You’re a brat and I'm not going let you be a bad influence on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp^.If only he knew what I did to his wife.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp^.Actually... I guess he does have good reason to worry about me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe^.I totally want to bang Naomi and Alia.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp^.I need to be careful though. That guy might just kill me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MlAnOp.Hurry up 1Hero. I don’t have all day.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EmBaEx.It’s a red plant. But it’s not like the green ginseng plants. The red ginseng is more rare.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.We’ll need to keep our eyes open. Which way should we go?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Ok Alia. Remember... Look sexy and I’ll be watching from the bushes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.It’ll make him fall asleep. Don’t worry Alia.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Oh god... This isn’t going to work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AbHaAg.By golly! Is that sexy young woman doing the Mississippi chicken dance?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AbFlAg.That bouncing booty needs a good spanking!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AbWoOp.Run dancing dame less you be stung as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Thank god. Now let’s get those love potions back to Emily.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlWoEx.We have to be careful who we sell these potions to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.Here you go 1Hero. Safety is just ahead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Thanks Michael. But I really want to find that bigfoot. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.You can return once the sun rises. I give you permission.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaDe.Well shit. The sun is up now. I haven’t slept a wink.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrCl.Oh, just hanging out in the park.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFlEx.Alia here is excited to go adventuring all the sudden.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFlOp.I think you’re rubbing off on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFrEx.As long as you are safe. Right 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFrOp.You know, when I was younger I loved to visit the park and swim in the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFlOp.On a hot summer day my friends and I loved hanging out in the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaSaOp.But these days you’re lucky if the park ranger doesn’t kick you out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnOp.Tell me about it. That guy can be a pain in the ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.But he did help me when I hit my head… So I guess I shouldn’t complain too much.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AlFrEx.Don’t hit your head silly. That’s where your thinking comes from.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFlOp.5Janet was asking some suspicious questions about you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NaFlOp.I’m sorry baby. But I think our little mess might be on 4Janets mind.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl^.Oh shit. I nearly forgot about that incident.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaDe^.No... That’s just what Naomi wants me to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Well I guess this is as good a place as any.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JaWoCl.I don’t know. Do you think we should be closer to the water? What’s he going to drink?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JaShEx.Of course it matters! You don’t want the thing to get dehydrated.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JaFrEx.Let’s let him go closer to the river.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Albert, wait! Don’t move! I have to shoot you with a tranquilizer dart.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.He’s going to get himself killed in the jungle! There are snakes, scorpions, jaguars, and who knows what else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.I need to make him stop moving for long enough to hit him with a dart... But how?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What bait would I use to lure him in close enough to tranquilize him?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Tasha. What the hell are you doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.I come to the park all the time. What are you doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.Are you trying to be a treasure hunter?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.It’s okay Tasha. You can have a nerdy hobby. No one will think any less of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.Too bad. Because I've found pieces of treasure here worth thousands of dollars.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnOp.How the hell do you know what they are worth?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I can’t give away that information Tasha. She’d get in big trouble.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlDe.So you’re selling illegally to a woman...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Oh god... Like tens of thousands it seems. In short order too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.You’ll never find anything with those techniques you were using.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaAnDe.Ok smart ass. How do you do it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaShOp.How much money will you get for it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Hey. I got a little lucky... But yeah. When you know what you’re looking for you can find some awesome treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Besides. You have to be careful digging here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoAg.Are you two illegally digging in the park!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlDe.Look who it is Corn. Baby Idaho decided to join us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoMaDe.You better watch your tongue kid. Or we’ll cut it off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlOp.I’m sure she wouldn’t mind if we just roughed you up a bit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JoFlOp.Aren’t the twins looking cute in their matching outfits?");
